<li id="cite_note-9"><b><a href="#cite_ref-9" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFMehta_MH2005">Mehta MH (2005). "Growth as a corrective force in the early treatment of progressive infantile scoliosis". <i>J Bone Joint Surg Br</i> <b>87</b> (9): 1237–47. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1302%2F0301-620X.87B9.16124" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.1302%2F0301-620X.87B9.16124" rel="nofollow">10.1302/0301-620X.87B9.16124</a></span>. <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/16129750" class="external" title="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/16129750">PMID 16129750</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Growth+as+a+corrective+force+in+the+early+treatment+of+progressive+infantile+scoliosis&amp;rft.jtitle=J+Bone+Joint+Surg+Br&amp;rft.aulast=Mehta+MH&amp;rft.au=Mehta+MH&amp;rft.date=2005&amp;rft.volume=87&amp;rft.issue=9&amp;rft.pages=1237%E2%80%9347&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.1302%2F0301-620X.87B9.16124&amp;rft_id=info:pmid/16129750&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Scoliosis"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
